# CI/CD & DevOps Guidelines

- **Monorepo**: Turborepo (`apps/web`, `apps/mobile`, `packages/common`)  
- **CI Workflow**: GitHub Actions – lint → unit → e2e (Playwright & Detox) → preview deploy  
- **Mobile Builds**: Expo EAS Build per platform  
- **Deployment**: blue-green for staging & production  
- **Monitoring**: Sentry (web & mobile), OpenTelemetry → Grafana
